Invocation Name: sakura haikus
des:
Sakura Haikus is glad to lighten up your mood with a short Japanese-style poem, a haiku.

Here are a few examples of what you can say:
Alexa, open Sakura Haikus.
Alexa, ask Sakura Haikus to read a poem.
Alexa, tell sakura haikus to entertain me.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
